item.title: Painful love
item.description: i love you so much, it hurts sometimes i think so much about you, i forget to breath sometimes i am so full of love for you, but feel so lonely sometimes i feel disoriented, lost and alone in this world i want you so bad, to bring you to my world i want so bad our worlds to merge help me, help me please, help me be better help me babe become sane and clean
